    "summary": "To contact me send an email to chris@chrisdesign.nl or give me a call at (+31) (0)6-24424204.\n\nI'm still a child at heart. Growing up, I truly loved building crazy Lego castles, playing way too tricky NES games, and being amazed by the fantastic plastic Transformers based on the Power Rangers. The fun and amazement of physical and digital play is still the most magical thing out there. \n\nToday I look to create and discover this spark of magic. Combined with the need to find simple, playful solutions to complex puzzles, the result is someone who likes to challenge themselves to create unique digital and physical experiences indoors and outdoors.",
